'''''Born of the Flickering''''' is the debut [[studio album]] by [[Norway|Norwegian]] [[extreme metal]] band [[Old Man's Child]]. It was released in 1995, through Hot Records.

In 1996, it was re-released through [[Century Media Records|Century Media]] with different artwork.

